DOC:
        * See the link below for an example of how to use myodbc with 
	unixODBC:
	http://www.unixodbc.org/doc/OOoMySQL.pdf

EXAMPLE:
        Configuration example of database called ALIX:

        * /etc/odbcinst.ini
	[MySQL]
	Description     = ODBC for mySQL
	Driver          = /usr/lib/libmyodbc3.so
	FileUsage       = 1

        * /etc/odbc.ini
	[MYSQL-example]
	Description     = Base de donnees example
	Driver          = MySQL
	Server          = localhost
	Database        = ALIX
	Port            = 3306

        * /home/ycrux/.odbc.ini
	[MYSQL-example]
        Description     = Base de donnees example
        Driver          = MySQL
        Server          = localhost
        Database        = ALIX
        Port            = 3306
